flowchart LR
  subgraph Data_Layer
    CSV[ml-latest CSV<br/>33.8M ratings + 14M tags]
    Parquet[Polars + Parquet<br/>partisi per-tahun 1995-2023]
    CSV --> Parquet
  end

  subgraph Feature_Store
    UF[user_features.parquet<br/>331K x 46 kolom]
    IF[item_features.parquet<br/>83K x 30 kolom]
    GE[genome_embedding.parquet<br/>1128-dim per film]
    SP[splits train/val/test<br/>leave-last-2-out]
    Parquet --> UF
    Parquet --> IF
    Parquet --> GE
    Parquet --> SP
  end

  subgraph Classical_Models
    BL[Baseline: GlobalMean / UserMean / ItemMean / Popularity]
    KN[Item-kNN / User-kNN cosine]
    MF[ALS / BPR / SVD-svds]
    CB[Content-based genome cosine]
    HY[Hybrid weighted alpha ALS + 1-alpha Content]
  end

  subgraph Deep_Models
    NCF[NCF: GMF + MLP + NeuMF]
    TT[Two-Tower: user/item encoder + FAISS IP]
    SR[SASRec transformer kausal]
  end

  subgraph NLP_Pipeline
    CL[Clean + lemmatize tags]
    BT[BERTopic 94 topik]
    ST[SBERT MiniLM 384-dim]
    UM[UMAP + HDBSCAN genome]
  end

  UF --> Classical_Models
  IF --> Classical_Models
  GE --> CB
  SP --> Classical_Models
  SP --> Deep_Models
  UF --> Deep_Models
  IF --> Deep_Models

  Classical_Models --> EV[Evaluator<br/>RMSE MAE NDCG MAP MRR<br/>Coverage Diversity Novelty Serendipity]
  Deep_Models --> EV
  NLP_Pipeline --> EV

  TT -->|export| ART[(two_tower_faiss.index<br/>user.npy / item.npy<br/>TorchScript)]
  ST -->|export| TXT[(movie_text.faiss<br/>384-dim)]

  ART --> API[FastAPI<br/>/health /recommend /similar<br/>/cold_start /semantic]
  TXT --> API
  API --> UI[Streamlit Dashboard<br/>EDA - Recommender - Search - Arena]
  API --> DOC[OpenAPI /docs]

  EV --> RP[reports/figures<br/>31 figur + CSV bench]
  RP --> PDF[portfolio_report.pdf]
